OL,5, A BBC employee who posted anti-Semitic 
OL,6, comments on social media has been      
OL,7, sacked by the corporation.             
OL,9,FDawn Queva, a BBC Three senior         
OL,10,Fscheduling coordinator, posted several 
OL,11,Fanti-Semitic comments on Facebook.     
OL,13,FThe BBC were made aware of these posts 
OL,14,Flast week, and on Sunday confirmed she 
OL,15,Fwas no longer an employee.             
OL,17,FIt said the corporation "does not      
OL,18,Ftolerate anti-Semitism, Islamophobia,  
OL,19,For any form of abuse, and we take any  
OL,20,Fsuch allegations seriously".           
